IMPORTANT — third-party material:
Individual records cite upstream sources. Government and operator filings,
press releases, and primary disclosures are facts and freely citable. Some
records also reference ANALYST material (e.g. SemiAnalysis, CBRE, Goldman,
LightCounting, TrendForce). Those underlying reports remain under their
owners' terms and are NOT relicensed by this CC BY 4.0 grant — each record's
`sources[].provenance` field marks which class it is. Re-users must honor the
original terms of any analyst source they rely on.

